com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel

Interface StreetLevelModel.OnEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StreetLevelModel.OnEventListener.OnEventListenerAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    StreetLevelModel

    public static interface StreetLevelModel.OnEventListener
    Represents a listener to provide notification upon completion of a StreetLevelModel event.
    See Also:
    StreetLevelModel.addStreetLevelModelListener(StreetLevelModel.OnEventListener)

      static class  StreetLevelModel.OnEventListener.OnEventListenerAdapter
